You have a sister, a
brother and a father.

39
00:02:24,230 --> 00:02:25,970
You have everything.

40
00:02:26,050 --> 00:02:28,400
- That thing is not my father.

41
00:02:28,490 --> 00:02:29,230
- Hush!

42
00:02:30,670 --> 00:02:32,710
And you, you have duties.

43
00:02:34,100 --> 00:02:36,110
You are neglecting them.

44
00:02:37,020 --> 00:02:38,670
You will change

45
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:43,070
or I will cut off the
limb that makes you sin.

46
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:46,120
[Fire crackling]

47
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:51,300
[Gentle music]

48
00:02:51,380 --> 00:02:53,470
- The yank, Yankees were driven

49
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:56,040
from cor, corinth by va, val-

50
