00:19:15,240 --> 00:19:18,060
- [Alan's sister] Stop
it, stop it right now.

275
00:19:18,150 --> 00:19:19,720
- [Gunner] Who's that?

276
00:19:19,810 --> 00:19:22,720
- You ghouls, you grave robbers.

277
00:19:22,810 --> 00:19:24,200
I'm warning you.

278
00:19:24,290 --> 00:19:26,680
There's a whole unit of
federals over that hill.

279
00:19:26,770 --> 00:19:30,990
What do you think they'll
do when they see this?

